8
00:01:44,969 --> 00:01:47,767
Dagger! I'll kill you, you hear?
Stick you like a pig.

9
00:01:50,809 --> 00:01:52,959
Ebony, Lula's freaked out...

10
00:01:53,129 --> 00:01:55,848
