502
00:44:19,729 --> 00:44:21,924
Pay what you owe!

503
00:44:27,009 --> 00:44:29,000
Don't drink that, it's blood!

504
00:44:31,929 --> 00:44:33,078
Shit!

505
00:44:34,529 --> 00:44:36,167
I thought it was water.

506
00:44:36,329 --> 00:44:40,242
Doctor, this guy was
sweating all night long.

507
00:44:40,409 --> 00:44:43,082
I've put him on antibiotics,
but if you ask me, it's no use.

508
00:44:43,249 --> 00:44:44,318
It's AIDS.

509
00:44:47,409 --> 00:44:48,728
Doctor!

510
00:44:50,529 --> 00:44:52,326
Who took away his oxygen?

511
00:44:55,089 --> 00:44:56,727
I don't want to die.

512
00:44:57,529 --> 00:45:01,078
