...six...

627
00:58:01,449 --> 00:58:02,723
...seven...

628
00:58:05,849 --> 00:58:07,202
...eight.

629
00:58:13,969 --> 00:58:15,482
Found it.

630
00:58:29,129 --> 00:58:30,642
So it's Visitors Day, is it?

631
00:58:32,169 --> 00:58:33,443
If you like...

632
00:58:33,769 --> 00:58:35,168
...you can go now.

633
00:58:47,849 --> 00:58:50,363
I've got a problem, I need to talk.

634
00:58:51,529 --> 00:58:53,281
This problem got a name?

635
00:58:53,809 --> 00:58:55,037
Ezequiel.

636
00:58:55,489 --> 00:58:58,401
He still owes me and now he's
trying to get more on account.

637
00:58:59,489 --> 00:59:02,799
He comes to my cell, raises his voice.
What's he playing at?

638
00:59:03,289 --> 00:59:05,200
-And you?
-Me?

639
00:59:05,929 --> 00:59:08,523
If I don't get paid,
I can't pay Highness.

640
00:59:09,609 --> 00:59:12,043
I want your permission
to kill the bastard.

641
00:59:12,369 --> 00:59:15,679
