674
01:01:59,609 --> 01:02:02,487
-Says who?
-Says no one. I saw her.

675
01:02:02,769 --> 01:02:05,841
They were making out in a squad car.

676
01:02:06,929 --> 01:02:08,806
Near the old bakery.

677
01:02:18,329 --> 01:02:20,081
Dina doesn't buy bread there.

678
01:02:20,249 --> 01:02:23,480
Miro, I saw her.
And it wasn't bread she was after.

679
01:02:31,249 --> 01:02:32,477
Celia...

680
01:02:33,969 --> 01:02:35,960
...is Antonio Carlos gay?

681
01:02:37,289 --> 01:02:39,086
What a question, Dina!

682
01:02:41,769 --> 01:02:46,445
He made up this story and told Miro
I've been going out with a cop.

683
01:02:46,609 --> 01:02:50,682
Like hell I made it up.
I saw you crawling all over him.

684
01:02:50,849 --> 01:02:55,365
-You nibbled his ear, damn it!
-Then it's me he's really after.

685
01:02:56,089 --> 01:02:58,683
You forgot the best part...

686
01:02:58,929 --> 01:03:02,080
...how you asked me to run away
with you...

687
01:03:02,249 --> 01:03:03,762
...and that I turned you down...

688
01:03:03,929 --> 01:03:05,681
...because I love my husband...

689
