695
01:03:33,609 --> 01:03:36,919
Celia, see if you can keep your man
around the house.

696
01:03:37,089 --> 01:03:39,683
I don't want him pestering me
in the street anymore.

697
01:03:43,049 --> 01:03:44,277
Miro!

698
01:03:49,209 --> 01:03:51,518
-Miro!
-Bastard! You dirty bastard!

699
01:03:51,849 --> 01:03:53,123
You've never fooled me.

700
01:03:53,289 --> 01:03:55,757
I always knew you had a crush on her.

701
01:03:55,929 --> 01:03:59,001
You can't even respect your
best friend's wife, you dog!

702
01:03:59,169 --> 01:04:00,966
-Calm down.
-Dog!

703
01:04:05,409 --> 01:04:08,526
Miro, I'm telling you the truth!

704
01:04:16,089 --> 01:04:17,920
I lost my friend and partner.

705
01:04:18,289 --> 01:04:21,440
The first robbery without him,
there were so many cops...

706
01:04:21,609 --> 01:04:23,839
...it looked more like a military parade.

707
01:04:24,169 --> 01:04:27,241
-What about him?
-I only found out when he got here.

708
01:04:27,609 --> 01:04:30,123
I thought I'd gone to hell, doctor.

709
01:04:30,289 --> 01:04:31,847
But him? I'll tell you.

710
01:04:32,289 --> 01:04:33,722
Come here, come on.

711
01:04:34,049 --> 01:04:35,448
