722
01:05:47,169 --> 01:05:49,478
We're taking the lot. Everything.

723
01:05:49,649 --> 01:05:51,446
Hand it over, the dough.
Come on, quick.

724
01:06:03,929 --> 01:06:07,922
Too bad, a smart guy like you
trusting his own wife.

725
01:06:08,569 --> 01:06:11,003
Some guys are born
to be cheated on.

726
01:06:26,889 --> 01:06:28,163
Are you all right?

727
01:06:49,609 --> 01:06:50,883
Doctor...

728
01:06:52,809 --> 01:06:58,884
...do infants remember
everything we do?

729
01:07:00,529 --> 01:07:03,441
No, not a thing.

730
01:07:05,609 --> 01:07:08,362
Doctor, let him go.

731
01:07:37,369 --> 01:07:38,927
And with you now...

732
01:07:39,089 --> 01:07:42,320
...our untamed diva of dance...

733
01:07:42,569 --> 01:07:45,686
...the woman who lives in all
thieves' hearts...

734
01:07:45,849 --> 01:07:50,604
...here at the detention center...

735
01:07:50,769 --> 01:07:55,923
...the one and only Rita Cadillac!

736
01:07:58,289 --> 01:08:00,644
-Rita!
-Rita!

737
01:08:46,529 --> 01:08:47,564
Hello!

738
01:08:48,489 --> 01:08:50,684
I know you all...

739
01:08:51,209 --> 01:08:54,758
...fool around a lot, right?

740
01:08:55,049 --> 01:08:56,482
Yes!

741
01:08:57,449 --> 01:08:59,917
But do you take care
of yourselves?

742
01:09:00,289 --> 01:09:01,563
Yes!

743
01:09:01,929 --> 01:09:06,241
Our friend, the doctor,
came here today...

744
01:09:06,409 --> 01:09:09,685
...and he's taught me enough
to teach you too, right?

745
01:09:09,849 --> 01:09:11,077
That's right!

746
01:09:11,369 --> 01:09:15,521
Okay, so some of you are
careful and some forget...

747
01:09:15,689 --> 01:09:19,045
