749
01:10:41,729 --> 01:10:45,119
-Dona Graca, Ebony sent you this.
-Thanks.

750
01:10:47,449 --> 01:10:51,647
-Oh, look. My man. Want some?
-No, thank you.

751
01:10:52,049 --> 01:10:54,768
See, Franci?
