Hey, get out!

1205
02:00:30,809 --> 02:00:32,720
I want to stay with you!

1206
02:02:01,809 --> 02:02:04,846
Sergeant, let's play
cops and robbers.

1207
02:02:43,889 --> 02:02:46,642
You're going to live
to tell the tale.

1208
02:02:58,529 --> 02:02:59,678
I changed my mind.

1209
02:03:25,489 --> 02:03:28,799
